<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Customizable Options for Branding</span></li></ol><p>Elevate your brand presence with custom printing or branding options available for our&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">paper bags</span>. Personalize each bag with your logo, slogan, or artwork to enhance brand recognition and create a lasting impression on customers.</p><ol><li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Biodegradable and Recyclable</span></li></ol><p>After use, our&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">paper bags</span>&nbsp;can be easily recycled or composted, minimizing waste and promoting a circular economy. Biodegradable materials ensure that even if disposed of improperly, these&nbsp;paper bags&nbsp;will naturally break down over time, leaving no harmful residue behind.</p>', 'Paper-Bags_The_deli_paper-1-1536x998.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', 'active', '2025-07-26 09:41:12', '2025-07-31 04:51:16', 'yes');
